{"tid":873020,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 去樓下茶記買咗個豆腐火腩飯","createTime":"2018-10-23T06:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T03:57:53.000Z","uid":33432,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6db725046f24c8b4ba2d8cb3940e4956253a959f","tid":873020,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日喺樓下間茶記叫咗個雙餸飯，30蚊<br />\n咁啱有豆腐火腩飯，就叫咗啦<br />\n滿心歡喜影咗張靚相，諗住連篇潮文post去facebook呃吓like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/143023_e4e14286248567d3e3d6ab63d069b74e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F143023_e4e14286248567d3e3d6ab63d069b74e.JPG&h=ef52f3cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n30蚊嚟講真係好ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦，當我一路食一路search緊篇潮文果陣，<br />\n發現啱啱不起舊豆腐有dd特別<br />\n佢色澤同普通豆腐一樣，但係佢背面<br />\n竟然 釀 咗 隻 小 強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/143248_aa86153952f0165fa14e38177068610c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F143248_aa86153952f0165fa14e38177068610c.jpg&h=497748dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺呢個決定香港存亡嘅危急關頭，喺咁有意義嘅豆腐火腩入面釀咗隻強，我相信，呢個係某d人托茶記俾我嘅特別暗示嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我望住隻強好耐，都諗唔到到底想我做d乜<br />\n<br />\n於是我冒住食過鐘嘅風險，走咗落去茶記，細細聲咁同個伙記講，<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;啱啱個豆腐火腩入面，有隻強喎&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n個伙記即刻擘大哂對原本無哂神嘅雙眼，用好堅定嘅眼神同我打開咗盒飯<br />\n<br />\n之後，佢一句sorry都無，就換咗第盒飯俾我<br />\n<br />\n窩蛋免治牛飯<br />\n<br />\n呢個又有咩含義呢？我係咪已經接近真相嘅核心？<br />\n<br />\n而家我坐喺公司，好驚有洗頭車嚟運我走，<br />\n<br />\n請問如何等待被運走而不失霸氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3a5a624cd3c12fc5f25bf758cb3a71f0a85b51","tid":873020,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:45:44.000Z","msg":"甲由讓豆腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a443c8dbe9d73211d93d38e8a4962683200b0036","tid":873020,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"豆腐強哥點都好過咖哩亞古獸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d21e28024834d7c92f108e5a51688547e086d96","tid":873020,"uid":124323,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"食得豆腐火腩飯我相信你都唔係一個膚淺既男人。樓主呢種男人應該係好似舊火腩咁，每一舊都經過高溫既千錘百煉。宜家只不過係隻曱甴讓左係舊豆腐入面，做男人咩風浪未見過？你有無見過地盤佬會怕曱甴？"},{"pid":"92c930406d4c4d971464581afe0f0b9f29609446","tid":873020,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d21e28024834d7c92f108e5a51688547e086d96","tid":873020,"uid":124323,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"食得豆腐火腩飯我相信你都唔係一個膚淺既男人。樓主呢種男人應該係好似舊火腩咁，每一舊都經過高溫既千錘百煉。宜家只不過係隻曱甴讓左係舊豆腐入面，做男人咩風浪未見過？你有無見過地盤佬會怕曱甴？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"無怕呀，不過我想知你係咪會食強㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我無呢個喜好，又懷疑有重大任務俾我，咪去回任囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cde89829d61bd2cd3bce1d7a20d47515ebf25fd","tid":873020,"uid":91631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢家野......"},{"pid":"d33d271b79369bc66fcc0f3cc0ecec807a5f4419","tid":873020,"uid":98847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"一陣窩蛋免治牛飯有隻蒼蠅係入面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c920fda2612b29659afd7d6ea0391796966a7468","tid":873020,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cde89829d61bd2cd3bce1d7a20d47515ebf25fd","tid":873020,"uid":91631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢家野......"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲講開爛gag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝讚賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73de11a6dd22de8e5959f817f08195e0920e87df","tid":873020,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d33d271b79369bc66fcc0f3cc0ecec807a5f4419","tid":873020,"uid":98847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"一陣窩蛋免治牛飯有隻蒼蠅係入面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"無呀咩都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9562c174da5312aaa7a10bee68f27406bc7a2efc","tid":873020,"uid":183525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"阿強已經碎左, 撈左落免治牛 ~"},{"pid":"316f49277d09fcda44c3755f51f7ca37034815ec","tid":873020,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"下次叫佢讓錢算啦， 仲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}